data.description: Beautiful open concept ranch ready to move right in. Interior features two bedrooms on main level with ample closet space. Primary bedroom is large with walk in closet. Primary bath has whirlpool tub, dual sinks and shower. 3rd Bdrm upstairs is non-conforming or could be an office. 4th bedroom in LL. Large kitchen with breakfast bar, granite counter tops, center island and canned lighting, yard professionally landscaped, covered porch. Large garage with storage. Close to shopping, schools and interstate. Check this one out. AMA
